values: This site is a great source of historical information about maenads et al. I was particularly amused on the page about Satyrs where it says "Their asses won the battle".

Hello, as this is my first journal entry, I will begin by giving you a brief statement about who I am and why I started this journal.
I am a 32 year old female, practicing non-wiccan witch and former sex worker. I started this journal as a way to discuss the more private aspects of my life anonymously but still explore the feedback others might have to offer. I call myself a maenad because Dionysus is the god I have always felt the most, although I am not a Greek Reconstructionist. I will elaborate more as this journal progresses.
Hello, this is my private (sort of) journal. I am still setting up housekeeping. Patience is a virtue...
